The android docs for the Calendar Provider are quite useful, but recommend the use of an AsyncQueryHandler for querying or adding events to calendars in an asynchronous thread. However the AsyncQueryHandler docs don&rsquo;t include much guidance as to how to use it.
To add an entry to an android calendar you first have to find out the calendar id using an asynchronous query on the calendars table.
